name: IaT
description: The secrets expressed in the ecstatic cry 'An-al-Haq' (I am Truth) as her ego dissolves and all that remains is pure radiance, will be punished by those who don't understand, and while people predictably react to this with the entire spectrum of familiar emotions; shock, horrow, awe, joy, even indifference and everything in between, my friend will be standing there hysterically laughing. Laughing, because my friend understands that there is no one left to persecute in the first place.
